\nLog 2.313 = n x log 1.15<br />\nn = log 2.313 / log 1.15 （㩒機搵答案）<br />\n<br />\n其實如果你諗到就直接出 n = log 細1.15 (大2.313)，細1.15係個base，答案用上面講左個個㩒法去搵，因為計數機個log base是10。<br />\n<br />\n其實你有禮貌d一早有人答左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，言行有時重要過成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：私補miss</blockquote><br />\n雖然你解答唔到我，不過都多謝你肯認真答我😘"},{"pid":"684fe8e659cc70e51c635baaad6a6103a6d5f3f1","tid":82710,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2.313=（1.15）^n<br />\n點樣5用log去搵個n出泥？求數神幫手</blockquote><br />\n2.313=（1.15）^n<br />\n1.15^n=1.15^n<br />\n1=1.15^n &divide; 1.15^n<br />\n1=(1.5/1.5)^n<br />\n1=1^n<br />\n<br />\nn=任何實數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 數學u"}]}